reviews.text: Averagely good quality. Should include egg by default for the price. Yuzu spicy soup was great and unique. Took a little too long (10min) for just some extra plain noodles. Usually they should come very quickly before the soup cools down. So order earlier if you can predict your hunger!

it feels average... nothing really impressive except the egg.
$78 ramen + $14 egg + 10%. the portion can be small for men. happy to see the red pickled sour ginger coz the soup is slightly gamey.
polite service.
clean.
just like many other ramen joints, you need to tick the boxes on a paper for your ramen. this is environment unfriendly.
Over priced that need to pay for the egg!! Taste is just ok and the air conditioning is so strong that it is like a freezer.
Although the price is a bit high, but the taste definitely worth it.
Just ok. Black garlic ramen + egg + Kirin = 137HKD. Card machines conveniently out for foreigners even though I have UnionPay. Still no. The couple immediately before us got to use their card.

Averagely good quality. Should include egg by default for the price. Yuzu spicy soup was great and unique. Took a little too long (10min) for just some extra plain noodles. Usually they should come very quickly before the soup cools down. So order earlier if you can predict your hunger!

美味九州拉麵，好多客人，地點都方便！
入到去，環境唔錯，好乾淨、簡單中有圓圓掛燈及白色花朵、花碟的裝飾！
拉麵價錢合理，有好幾種不同湯底選擇，我們選了1. 招牌叉燒濃豚骨湯拉麵2. 白雞湯豚肉拉麵（我們加了粟米粒粒、芽菜、糖芯蛋）
好好味呀，唔咸、拉麵滑、豚肉好腍又香！
